.SH NAME
.PP
waybar - idle_inhibitor module
.PP
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The \fBidle_inhibitor\fR module can inhibit the idle behavior such as screen blanking, locking, and
screensaver, also known as "presentation mode".\&
.PP
